MobBountyReloaded is a new and updated version of MobBounty.

For support and help, go to: http://dev.bukkit.org/server-mods/mobbountyreloaded/

Commands:

Permissions:
    shadows.*:
        description: All Shadows permissions.
        children:
            shadows.disappear: true
            shadows.immunity: true
            shadows.see: true
    shadows.disappear:
        description: Allows player to disappear and reappear.
        default: op
    shadows.immunity:
        description: Player won't receive damage while invisible.
        default: op
    shadows.see:
        description: Player can see all vanished players.
        default: op